m/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rob-mcelhenney-ryan-reynolds@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rob-mcelhenney-ryan-reynolds@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rob-mcelhenney-ryan-reynolds@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rob-mcelhenney-ryan-reynolds@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rob-mcelhenney-ryan-reynolds@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞恩·雷诺兹 (Ryan Reynolds)</a>公开了为什么他必须删掉<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/deadpool-and-wolverine"><em>《死侍与金刚狼》</em></a>中罗布·麦克尔亨尼 (Rob McElhenney) 的客串 - 详情请见下文。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="442" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/deadpool-wolverine-review-marvel-3777877"><b>《死侍与金刚狼》评论：一部尖酸刻薄、跨越时空的超级英雄讽刺剧</b></a></li></ul><p><em>《死侍与金刚狼》</em>上映后不久，与雷诺兹共同拥有威尔士雷克斯汉姆 AFC 足球队的罗布·麦克尔亨尼 (Rob McElhenney) 透露， <a href="https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a61724101/rob-mcelhenney-deadpool-and-wolverine-cameo-cut/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他曾为漫威超级英雄电影拍摄过一段客串，但由于未知原因被剪掉了</a>。</p><p>现在，近一个月后，雷诺兹透露了麦克尔亨尼的场景最终被取消的原因。雷诺兹周末在 Instagram 上写道：“关于我的“亲爱的”朋友@robmcelhenney 的一句话。罗布非常友善地在#DeadpoolAndWolverine 中客串，希望这将继续出现在数字临时演员中。” </p><figure id="attachment_3778792" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3778792" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3778792" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer.jpg" alt="《死侍与金刚狼》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3778792" class="wp-caption-text"> 《死侍与金刚狼》。图片来源：漫威</figcaption></figure><p>“在剪辑电影时，他们说你“有时必须杀死你的宝贝。”怀着沉重的心情（并且通过外部的大力干预），我不得不用这个客串杀死一个心爱的人……”</p><p>他接着解释道：“这个序列并没有按照我们最初构建的方式运行。罗伯是它能在剪辑中停留这么久的唯一原因，因为即使在 TVA 面具和头盔下，你也能感觉到他在燃烧着原始的、几乎无限的才华、作家的智慧和“我创作热门电视节目”。 ”大摇大摆。甚至不要让我开始雷克瑟姆。如果没有 Rob McElhenney，我不会知道像 @wrexham_afc 这样的爱。”</p><p>雷诺兹随后详细谈到了麦克尔亨尼的朋友类型，他说罗布专程飞到伦敦来客串，他对不得不完全剪掉这场戏感到“羞愧”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_BM0caxcpP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin